law.history: Repealed 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 469, sec. 40, effective July 15, 1994. -- Repealed, reenacted and amended as KRS 151B.135, 1990 Ky. Acts ch. 470, sec. 26, effective July 1, 1990. -- Amended 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 179, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1988 as KRS 158.790. -- Created 1985 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 10, sec. 23, effective October 18, 1985.

metadata.lrc-note: (7/13/90) The subsequent repeal, with reenactment and amendment, of this section prevails over its amendment by a prior Act of the 1990 Regular Session pursuant to KRS 446.260.
